 \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"foot\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"woolly mammoths\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"saber-toothed cats\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"giant deer\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"the land\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the climate warmed and the Ice Age ended, forests began to spread across the area, providing a habitat for many more familiar-looking animals that we can still see in some areas today.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the climate\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ice Age\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"forests\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"a habitat\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"many more familiar-looking animals\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"some areas\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Humans did not arrive in Paris until about 12,000 years ago.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999386091, \"rank\": 6.11670336132543e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Humans\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These early inhabitants were hunter-gatherers who lived off the land, hunting animals and gathering fruits and nuts from the forests.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These early inhabitants\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"hunter-gatherers\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"the land\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"animals\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"fruits\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"nuts\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"the forests\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As time passed, these nomadic tribes began to settle, and agricultural practices started.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"these nomadic tribes\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"agricultural practices\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was just the start of the next major shift in the Paris landscape.\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3029, \"end\": 3034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999386091, \"rank\": 6.11670336132543e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the start\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"the next major shift\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By around 250 B.C., a Celtic tribe known as the Parisii established a settlement on the \\u00cele de la Cit\\u00e9, an island in the middle of the Seine River.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3061, \"end\": 3065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anno_Domini\", \"score\": 0.9999999545193542, \"rank\": 4.548079070961641e-08, \"text\": \"B.C.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anno_Domini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anno_Domini\"}, {\"begin\": 3069, \"end\": 3075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celts\", \"score\": 0.9999999993815436, \"rank\": 6.078046149923529e-10